trans-unit.source: Defines a key/value pair in an <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract"></xref>.
Initializes an instance of the <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry"></xref> structure with the specified key and value.
trans-unit.target: Initialiseert een exemplaar van de <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry"> </xref> structuur met de opgegeven sleutel en waarde.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument"></xref> that contains the key in the new <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: De <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument"> </xref> bevat die de sleutel in het nieuwe <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument"></xref> that contains the value in the new <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: De <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument"> </xref> bevat die de waarde in het nieuwe <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Represents the key in the key/value pair that this <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Hiermee geeft u de sleutel in de sleutelwaarde koppelt die dit <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry"> </xref> vertegenwoordigt.

trans-unit.source: Represents the value in the key/value pair that this <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Geeft de waarde in de sleutelwaarde koppelt die dit <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry"> </xref> vertegenwoordigt.
